            "creation_date": 1422040674,
            "body": "<p>Get it as an int column :<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>int count = -1;\nif (rs.next()) {\n    count = rs.getInt(1);\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 28117127,
            "question_id": 28117116
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/02d65d10806e6a5cdf8989de025ce3ad?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
